Package: AGCA4extremes
Title: Anchored Geodesic Component Analysis for Extremes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alberto", "Quaini", email = "alberto91quaini@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements anchored geodesic component analysis for multivariate
    extremes. The package provides Pareto and rank-Pareto marginal
    standardization, top-k angular extraction, anchored eigensolutions,
    reconstruction, diagnostics, nonparametric bootstrap tools, and plotting
    methods for benchmark-relative angular variation.
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: C++17
URL: https://github.com/a91quaini/AGCA4extremes
BugReports: https://github.com/a91quaini/AGCA4extremes/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    Rcpp,
    stats
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
